tps://i.ytimg.com/vi_webp/hPXvawFwtjs/hqdefault.webp", "preference": -6, "id": "35"}, {"url": "https://i.ytimg.com/vi/hPXvawFwtjs/sddefault.jpg", "height": 480, "width": 640, "preference": -5, "id": "36", "resolution": "640x480"}, {"url": "https://i.ytimg.com/vi_webp/hPXvawFwtjs/sddefault.webp", "preference": -4, "id": "37"}, {"url": "https://i.ytimg.com/vi/hPXvawFwtjs/hq720.jpg", "preference": -3, "id": "38"}, {"url": "https://i.ytimg.com/vi_webp/hPXvawFwtjs/hq720.webp", "preference": -2, "id": "39"}, {"url": "https://i.ytimg.com/vi/hPXvawFwtjs/maxresdefault.jpg", "height": 1080, "width": 1920, "preference": -1, "id": "40", "resolution": "1920x1080"}, {"url": "https://i.ytimg.com/vi_webp/hPXvawFwtjs/maxresdefault.webp", "preference": 0, "id": "41"}], "thumbnail": "https://i.ytimg.com/vi/hPXvawFwtjs/maxresdefault.jpg", "description": "https://www.loopmasters.com/genres/168-Melodic-Techno/products/10346-TD-Audio-Melodic-Techno\nWe put together another amazing Techno collection based on Melodic vibes. Techno Changes quite a bit over time. Adding melodies over heavy grooving beats is more than fashion its essential when moving a crowd in and out of different tracks to keep them grooving and moving all night long.\nTD Audio presents our first Melodic Techno collection. This in house sample creation puts our twist on this current trend in Techno music.  Our newest collection is made form the ground up giving you a fresh new perspective to this chart topping style. This pack has just over 1GB of pure content.\nWe deliver our custom Drum sounds. Expect to find juicy kicks and percussion sounds. Groovy Top Loops and modern Techno Drum Loops to fire up your next back beat. This latest 24 Bit endeavor also includes Fx which we all love to drop in our music.\nMelodic Techno of course includes all the essential Melodic sounds you crave. This pack offers you a nice selection of Arps, Bass Loops, Atmos, Pads and of course Synth Loops.  Everything you hear in the demo is in the pack.\nThis collection features Melody Loops to use as is or just mangle them up with your own sounds. We added Midi Files to help you get this done with ease.  Not Bad hey.\nIf you are into Melodic Techno we think our latest take on it, is really gonna boost your creative juices in a big way. This pack is 100% License Free and can be used with or without your music. Just have fun and create your next Melodic Techno Hit.\nMelodies included.", "channel_id": "UCePzmuJTIni6OwQVq8egttA", "channel_url": "https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCePzmuJTIni6OwQVq8egttA", "duration": 218, "view_count": 1144, "age_limit": 0, "webpage_url": "https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=hPXvawFwtjs", "categories": ["Music"], "tags": ["sampling music", "music production", "loopmasters", "presets", "music producer", "make electronic music", "hard dance", "make EDM", "TD Audio", "techno", "tech house", "tek house", "hardcore", "edm", "music Fx", "24 bit", "sample free sounds", "sample pack"], "playable_in_embed": true, "live_status": "not_live", "media_type": "video", "_format_sort_fields": ["quality", "res", "fps", "hdr:12", "source", "vcodec", "channels", "acodec", "lang", "proto"], "automatic_captions": {}, "subtitles": {}, "comment_count": 2, "like_count": 23, "channel": "Industrial Strength Records", "channel_follower_count": 18100, "uploader": "Industrial Strength Records", "uploader_id": "@IndustrialStrengthNY", "uploader_url": "https://www.youtube.com/@IndustrialStrengthNY", "upload_date": "20200122", "timestamp": 1579698259, "availability": "public", "webpage_url_basename": "watch", "webpage_url_domain": "youtube.com", "extractor": "youtube", "extractor_key": "Youtube", "display_id": "hPXvawFwtjs", "fulltitle": "SAMPLE PACK - Melodic Techno TDAudio", "duration_string": "3:38", "is_live": false, "was_live": false, "epoch": 1783691408, "asr": 48000, "filesize": 3746207, "format_id": "251", "format_note": "medium", "source_preference": -1, "audio_channels": 2, "quality": 3.0, "has_drm": false, "